I'm trying to use custom type as route parameter, but I'm getting error "Specified cast is not valid." in the browser.
Similar approach is used on server-side controllers and it works flawlessly. Am I doing something wrong?

### Expected Behavior

The custom type have `TypeConverter` that is able to convert from string, so there should not be "Specified cast is not valid." error at all.

### Steps To Reproduce

